if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb99af58f35b78750346b101370bf0958bffa10","tid":608551,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c6d1b39a53729fbf10724f56e9814c870fe4f7","tid":608551,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d54ad5809be058c4c98d7df3453512bf9df9330","tid":608551,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"第二個係？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"李思捷/鄺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"老屈完未?"},{"pid":"50f774ee8a973468e56479bb8356ce8562b08b00","tid":608551,"uid":166749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:48:40.000Z","msg":"真心唔覺得佢地搞笑"},{"pid":"a923f3b4afbc405a20fb42e544f59a9008b35179","tid":608551,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> dickson啲轉數勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毛記葵涌（1716）今日上市，專家Dickson被委以重任，成為毛記發言人，不但代表上台發言，敲鑼，更加接受記者訪問，而專家Dickson全程妙問膠答。<br />\n<br />\n被問到預期股價走勢有冇驚喜，「100毛上到市都係一個驚喜，所以我估個走勢都應該驚喜。」<br />\n<br />\n被問對公司前景有冇信心，「嘩！雖然我個名目係『財經投資專家』，但其實我係一個『愛情財經投資專家』，我只能夠講，我自己希望，我自己愛情指數會上升。」<br />\n<br />\n被問公司上市後有何變化，「我估雪櫃發霉食物會清理咗佢。」<br />\n<br />\n被問公司上市後會否爭取加人工，「我每一日都爭取，最好日日加畀我。」<br />\n<br />\n被問老細會否對他予以獎勵，「我相信係會嘅，但我希望唔會係獎兩巴掌。」<br />\n<br />\n被問會否想公司派予股份，「公司其實有架，佢哋派咗兩股畀我，就係東方昇嗰兩股。你哋有冇睇東方昇特異功能救香港，嚟緊會有門票畀我哋，嚟緊加場呀4月3號賣飛。」<br />\n<br />\n被問毛記多人抽原因，「好多人抽我哋隻新股咩？哦，點解會咁多人抽，可能係因為100毛個100好意頭。」<br />\n<br />\n被問今日有咩慶祝活動，「我諗就係返工。」<br />\n<br />\n被問嚟緊會唔會再搞多啲大型Show，「我相信會、我相信會。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到公司業績前景，「公司有業績架咩，我自己估計，應該係ok。我諗呢啲你真係問返啲投資專家，我只係一個『愛情財經投資專家』，仲要係一個失敗嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n被問未來會否與中資公司合作拍廣告，「你係咪講中立嘅資金？（內地嘅資金）我諗應該唔會。」<br />\n<br />\n被問未來會否與信用卡推出大型廣告，「呢樣我真係唔知，我喺公司係斟吓水，幫人整吓電腦。」<br />\n<br />\n作為員工，覺得老細今日心情點，「一貫作風，都係黑面，冇咩特別。」<br />\n<br />\n最後終於有記者忍唔住問，「你哋公司會唔會有其他人，講到啲實際啲嘅嘢？」Dickson指，「我諗有嘅，我哋公司都OK嘅。」"},{"pid":"efc42507e86b6cba8a5b98266195563d9b5fb7e8","tid":608551,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cb99af58f35b78750346b101370bf0958bffa10","tid":608551,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c6d1b39a53729fbf10724f56e9814c870fe4f7","tid":608551,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d54ad5809be058c4c98d7df3453512bf9df9330","tid":608551,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"第二個係？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"李思捷/鄺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"老屈完未?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"係你有新狙擊目標姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家連南珠都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2da4a2ac4b541a9a3f79e937bb0f2fa3d61ee80","tid":608551,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efc42507e86b6cba8a5b98266195563d9b5fb7e8","tid":608551,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cb99af58f35b78750346b101370bf0958bffa10","tid":608551,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c6d1b39a53729fbf10724f56e9814c870fe4f7","tid":608551,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"李思捷/鄺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h